    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【官方qq群：137901682】<br>【定期发放福利回馈玩家】</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《洛菲水族馆》是一款提高工作专注度的工具游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每次完成番茄时钟，就能获得一堆番茄的奖励，一边工作一边养鱼，获得的番茄奖励可以提高鱼的成长速度。你越努力工作，你的鱼儿成长越快。你也能获得越多的装饰品或深海的水草。你可以利用鱼儿赚的钱打造一个属于自己独一无二的鱼缸。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >购买鱼苗包，解锁稀有鱼种！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当你工作时，鱼会慢慢长大，当它们成熟时，你可以卖掉它们来赚取硬币，这些硬币可以用来抽取更多的新鱼（这个过程是随机的）。你也可以养这些鱼来收集它们，给它们命名，抚摸它们，并加深你与它们的联系。甚至建立一个单一品种的鱼群。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051380/extras/0b266136d6d58c63f17618e9b1acc57e.poster.avif?t=1766829783\" width=620 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051380/extras/0b266136d6d58c63f17618e9b1acc57e.webm?t=1766829783\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051380/extras/0b266136d6d58c63f17618e9b1acc57e.mp4?t=1766829783\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >内置实用的生产工具：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >内置了精心挑选的lofi音乐，自定义的白噪音，番茄种和工作清单，每次完成番茄时间可以获得番茄。给与你正反馈激励。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以将其与低保真音乐和平静的白噪音自由搭配，例如冥想、专注的细雨声或电影胶片声音，帮助你进入高效工作的状态。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051380/extras/469edb1bb66026c8befaef00d044ce86.poster.avif?t=1766829783\" width=620 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051380/extras/469edb1bb66026c8befaef00d044ce86.webm?t=1766829783\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051380/extras/469edb1bb66026c8befaef00d044ce86.mp4?t=1766829783\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>在你工作闲暇的时候喂食你的小鱼，数百种精致稀有的鱼类等待你解锁。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >丰富的场景</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >搭配lofi音乐，为你提供适合自己的专注空间。例如宇航员来到了一个奇异的空间，在这个空间中，有个戴着头盔在弹钢琴的孩子，并且他身后凭空多了一把伞。这可能是一个会满足人愿望的星球。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051380/extras/e66479d8ac3669f36c41882cd99267b8.poster.avif?t=1766829783\" width=620 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051380/extras/e66479d8ac3669f36c41882cd99267b8.webm?t=1766829783\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051380/extras/e66479d8ac3669f36c41882cd99267b8.mp4?t=1766829783\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >专注工作的正反馈</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >积累了足够的番茄可以让你获得装饰品奖励，并组合出你独一无二的鱼缸</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051380/extras/654f055be7c5fe41e5d286f54c9d0cd4.poster.avif?t=1766829783\" width=620 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051380/extras/654f055be7c5fe41e5d286f54c9d0cd4.webm?t=1766829783\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051380/extras/654f055be7c5fe41e5d286f54c9d0cd4.mp4?t=1766829783\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >在你的工作设备上，自由地调整鱼缸大小</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051380/extras/1212910b504b05b8e70e5837128fceb3.poster.avif?t=1766829783\" width=620 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051380/extras/1212910b504b05b8e70e5837128fceb3.webm?t=1766829783\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051380/extras/1212910b504b05b8e70e5837128fceb3.mp4?t=1766829783\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >还有更多的内容等待你的探索。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 大量的鱼类品种等待你的解锁。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 来自番茄时钟的正反馈，工作越努力，获得越多的番茄。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 不断扩大鱼缸空间，养更多的鱼。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 增加鱼缸的数量，获得更多的游戏体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 带有隐藏故事的场景空间。太空的钢琴师，沙漏的秘密，水下的等等</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 数十种可以自由组合的背景白噪音。能搭配属于自己的沉浸工作状态。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 数十种Lo-fi音乐，Lo-fi音乐其独特的孤独感和疏离感，安慰着都市寂寞的人群。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 放置成长的玩法，不断积累给你带来成就感。</p>",
